{"tid":995754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★江蘇出土700年前宋元棺木　「立立令」驚呆網民：這剛下葬嗎？","createTime":"2019-01-25T16:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T04:55:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"396ac03602137f75862b04b8ea4924d36781f9b5","tid":995754,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2343943/org/f091c2e3084709b34a9180aa31c2de92.jpg/z981SB3JqKsjYc2a4Vjgc0VV2G-yhspLmqNOW5qjTls?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2343943%2Forg%2Ff091c2e3084709b34a9180aa31c2de92.jpg%2Fz981SB3JqKsjYc2a4Vjgc0VV2G-yhspLmqNOW5qjTls%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=985f7b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江蘇常州唐陵村早前進行工程時，意外在現場發現一個宋元年代的磚室墓群。不過令考古人員驚訝的是，出土的棺木竟保存得相當好，紅色的外觀仍舊閃閃發亮，彷彿才剛漆好一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2343143/org/a0f80e2f76de20063b467a3a1a836c27.jpg/h_BkBVESqdCKo__9Qn1bN0XLB9aFXMqLczVmUHM1ZlA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2343143%2Forg%2Fa0f80e2f76de20063b467a3a1a836c27.jpg%2Fh_BkBVESqdCKo__9Qn1bN0XLB9aFXMqLczVmUHM1ZlA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=c7a99378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「青膏泥」助保存<br />\n<br />\n考古小組一共在現場發掘到3處磚室墓，並將它們依照位置由右向左編號為M1至M3，其中M1受到施工機械的破損最為嚴重，墓頂頂磚已經坍塌，其次是M2因為埋藏的深度較深，僅遭到了部分破壞，至於M3則受輕微破壞。<br />\n<br />\n據專家分析，M2很可能是一座元代早期下葬的古墓，不過由於M2墓葬結構保存完整，加上磚室與木棺間填充大量「青膏泥」，導致棺木保存相當良好，紅色外觀還閃閃發亮，就像剛漆好的一樣，相當罕見。考古小組最後決定採用木方、海綿、繃帶等固定棺木，再由起降機吊到重型卡車上，一路將它運回博物館地下庫房進行保護。<br />\n<br />\n陵墓主人或曾經歷宋元更替<br />\n<br />\n此外，考古小組也在M1、M3出土了26件文物，包含2件瓷器、14件金銀器、5件木器等文物，其中M3所出土的錢幣是「至大通寶」，為元武宗時期（約西元1310-1311年）所鑄造發行，因此專家推測，陵墓主人可能經歷由宋朝至元朝的朝代更替。<br />\n<br />\n網民們看見這幾張棺木照片後，紛紛直呼 「青膏泥到底是甚麼好東西，這防腐朽的能力未免也太強」、「這顏色真的太新了吧，裡面的主人會不會也是剛下葬的樣子，換作是我都不太敢打開來」、「這來自元朝？你跟我說這是幾天後才要準備下葬的我都信」、「打開來，裡面主人會不會說哈嘍」、「有沒有開棺的影片，想知道裡面到底長怎樣」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A1%8C%E8%B5%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/285015/%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F700%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%AE%8B%E5%85%83%E6%A3%BA%E6%9C%A8-%E7%AB%8B%E7%AB%8B%E4%BB%A4-%E9%A9%9A%E5%91%86%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E9%80%99%E5%89%9B%E4%B8%8B%E8%91%AC%E5%97%8E?fbclid=IwAR2Y-yh4-YqNsC8jiDs9lJa-vyM6tP3liUf7qLdGIrhtVL_Ki5qEl7ZAO0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F285015%2F%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8%2598%2587%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%259C%259F700%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25AE%258B%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%25A3%25BA%25E6%259C%25A8-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E7%25AB%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E9%25A9%259A%25E5%2591%2586%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%2589%259B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%2591%25AC%25E5%2597%258E%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2Y-yh4-YqNsC8jiDs9lJa-vyM6tP3liUf7qLdGIrhtVL_Ki5qEl7ZAO0w&d=%2Bt8JJVZzEYN6%2Bh2Lyu1Zb%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6e0f934d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A1%8C%E8%B5%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/285015/%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F700%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%AE%8B%E5%85%83%E6%A3%BA%E6%9C%A8-%E7%AB%8B%E7%AB%8B%E4%BB%A4-%E9%A9%9A%E5%91%86%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E9%80%99%E5%89%9B%E4%B8%8B%E8%91%AC%E5%97%8E?fbclid=IwAR2Y-yh4-YqNsC8jiDs9lJa-vyM6tP3liUf7qLdGIrhtVL_Ki5qEl7ZAO0w</a>"},{"pid":"fb71d315575e788c13eb8905aa272318ea09428c","tid":995754,"uid":19454,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KGGOOk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KGGOOk.jpg&h=1dd164cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a08c8a8475f7b23eba91af517f722ea97debb1ee","tid":995754,"uid":132128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:56:19.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ec1290694d552a0ab2d05b159082495a26f04d","tid":995754,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s